---
title: Almond & Chimichurri Crusted Pork with Zesty Roast Veggie Toss & Garlic Yoghurt
description: Sunset roasted veggies and pork loin steaks seasoned with chimichurri is a colourful combination of flavours. Dollop
over a cooling serve of garlic yoghurt to finish off the dish. At the end of the rainbow is a reward of almonds crusted on top of the pork to add a hint of nuttiness.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

